General Accountant- Iraq
- ,
Date Posted: 2014/05/02 06:25:40
Ref. JB3046577
Job Description
1-	Handle petty cash and record according vouchers.
2-	Customers accounting:
a.	Invoicing
b.	Collection
3-	Suppliers and related party accounting.
4-	Bank and cash accounting:
a.	Monthly bank & cash reconciliation
5-	Inventory accounting, local and foreign purchases, with inventory transactions and costing.
6-	Generate standard monthly and other needed reporting as:
a.	Bank & Cash situation
b.	Aging for : Inventory, Customers, Suppliers.
c.	Top line or Sales by brand, by area, by sales rep, by customer.
7-	Elaborate a monthly and up-to-date accurate trial balance.
8-	Deal with banks, lawyer, auditors and IT support.
9-	Maintain the financial modules in the ERP Navision.
Skills
•	BA in business administration, Accounting or Finance
•	2-3 years experience in general accounting
•	Ability to deal with numbers
•	Good interpersonal and communication skills
•	Good organizational and analytic skills
•	Attention to details and accuracy
