About This Company
HOLDAL’s proud roots were firmly planted in 1947, when Georges Abou Adal established his first company, Georges Abou Adal & Cie.
The business consisted of the import and distribution of watches and pharmaceuticals in Lebanon and in Syria.
To cater to the growing companies of Abou Adal Group, HOLDAL s.a.l. was established in 1992 as the Group’s Holding Company.
Today, HOLDAL s.a.l. not only boasts a distinguished portfolio of brands, but also a dedicated staff of 590 highly experienced professionals.
The Company is recognized for its strong and established network of distribution and retail, its market, manufacturing and services knowledge.
The Group is actively present in Lebanon, Syria and Iraq.
